csdl.jupiter.event
Class ReviewIssueModelEvent

java.lang.Object
  csdl.jupiter.event.ReviewIssueModelEvent

public class ReviewIssueModelEvent
extends java.lang.Object

Provides review issue model event. This wraps review issue entry with an event type. This is used for the argument of the reviewIssueModelChanged in the IReviewIssueModelListener interface.

Version:
$Id: ReviewIssueModelEvent.java,v 1.9 2005/03/28 14:39:31 takuyay Exp $
Author:
Takuya Yamashita
